    <description>Package Description</description>
    <releaseNotes>'Merged PR 10583: update Readme on Read/Write Optype Setup'
'Merged PR 10477: [DFF] Capability to read from UBE in case of duplicates for Dummy Die with ULT as EMPTY'
'Merged PR 10346: adding DLE check and update the strgval truncate value'
'Merged PR 10200:  New set of API to search for tokens within VID level. New param for PrimeGetDffTestMethod to utilize new API behavior.'
'Merged PR 10080: [HDBI][PrimeDffFooterPrintTestMethod] Capability to print MTL into ITUFF'
'Merged PR 9613: [DFF] Fixed stack die delimiter'
'Merged PR 9574: Merged PR 9487: [DffService] Fix GetAllWriteableTokensForCurrentOptype error without TIME token rules in MTL'</releaseNotes>
    <copyright>Copyright (2005) (2025) Intel Corporation</copyright>
